dc_title_s: Yeendoo Nanh Nakhweenjit K'atr'ahanahtyaa: Environmental change and traditional use of the Old Crow Flats in northern Canada
dc_description_s: This multidisciplinary project is comprised of eight components focusing on: geology and Paleoenvironments (Froese); hydrology and biology (Wolfe); permafrost (Burn); dendrochronology (Pisaric); vegetation (Lantz); food security (Chan); muskrat (Humphries); and moose (Cooley).
